items.question: What style of beer got the most page views last month?
items.sql:
SELECT
  topic_wiki.name AS name,
  SUM(requests) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    topic.mid AS mid,
    topic.name AS name,
    REPLACE(REPLACE(wiki.title, '$0028', '('), '$0029', ')') AS title
  FROM (
    SELECT
      mid,
      name
    FROM
      [freebase_tags.beer_types]) topic
  JOIN (
    SELECT
      REGEXP_REPLACE(REGEXP_REPLACE(obj, '/wikipedia/en/', ''), '/wikipedia/id/', '') AS title,
      sub AS mid
    FROM
      [fh-bigquery:freebase20140119.triples_nolang]
    WHERE
      obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/en'
      OR obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/id'
      AND pred = '/type/object/key') wiki
  ON
    wiki.mid = topic.mid) topic_wiki
JOIN
  [fh-bigquery:wikipedia.pagecounts_201602] views
ON
  views.title = topic_wiki.title
GROUP BY
  mid,
  name
ORDER BY
  total DESC
LIMIT
  10
IGNORE CASE

items.question: Which country was most mentioned in relation to England?
items.sql:
SELECT
  other.country,
  COUNT(*) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    ccode,
    other
  FROM (
    SELECT
      Actor1Code AS ccode,
      Actor2Code AS other,
      Year
    FROM
      [gdelt-bq:full.events]) cc1,
    (
    SELECT
      Actor1Code AS other,
      Actor2Code AS ccode,
      Year
    FROM
      [gdelt-bq:full.events]) cc2
  WHERE
    Year = 2015) events
JOIN
  [gdelt-bq:extra.countryinfo] country
ON
  country.iso3 = events.ccode
JOIN
  [gdelt-bq:extra.countryinfo] other
ON
  events.other = other.iso3
WHERE
  country.country = 'England'
GROUP BY
  country.country,
  other.country
ORDER BY
  total DESC

  FROM

GROUP BY

ORDER BY

items.question: Which programming language winks the most?
items.sql:
SELECT
  repos.repository_language,
  SUM(CASE WHEN REGEXP_MATCH(JSON_EXTRACT(payload, '$.comment.body'), r'(?i)\b()\b') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 1000 / COUNT(*) AS per,
  COUNT(*) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM
    TABLE_QUERY([githubarchive:month], 'table_id like "2016%"')
  WHERE
    type = 'IssueCommentEvent') AS comments
JOIN (
  SELECT
    CONCAT(repository_owner, '/', repository_name) AS repository_name,
    repository_language
  FROM
    [githubarchive:github.timeline]
  WHERE
    repository_language IS NOT NULL
  GROUP BY
    repository_language,
    repository_name) repos
ON
  repos.repository_name = comments.repo_name
GROUP BY
  repos.repository_language
HAVING
  total > 50000
ORDER BY
  per DESC
LIMIT
  10 IGNORE CASE

items.question: Which country was most mentioned in relation to Turkey?
items.sql:
SELECT
  other.country,
  COUNT(*) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    ccode,
    other
  FROM (
    SELECT
      Actor1Code AS ccode,
      Actor2Code AS other,
      Year
    FROM
      [gdelt-bq:full.events]) cc1,
    (
    SELECT
      Actor1Code AS other,
      Actor2Code AS ccode,
      Year
    FROM
      [gdelt-bq:full.events]) cc2
  WHERE
    Year = 2015) events
JOIN
  [gdelt-bq:extra.countryinfo] country
ON
  country.iso3 = events.ccode
JOIN
  [gdelt-bq:extra.countryinfo] other
ON
  events.other = other.iso3
WHERE
  country.country = 'Turkeyl'
GROUP BY
  country.country,
  other.country
ORDER BY
  total DESC
IGNORE CASE

  repos.repository_name = comments.repo_name
GROUP BY
  repos.repository_language
HAVING
  total > 50000
ORDER BY
  per DESC
LIMIT
  10 IGNORE CASE
items.inputSQL:
SELECT
  repos.repository_language,
  SUM(CASE WHEN REGEXP_MATCH(JSON_EXTRACT(payload, '$.comment.body'), r'(?i)\b()\b') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 1000 / COUNT(*) AS per,
  COUNT(*) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM
    TABLE_QUERY([githubarchive:month], 'table_id like "2016%"')
  WHERE
    type = 'IssueCommentEvent') AS comments
JOIN (
  SELECT
    CONCAT(repository_owner, '/', repository_name) AS repository_name,
    repository_language
  FROM
    [githubarchive:github.timeline]
  WHERE
    repository_language = 'userInput'
  GROUP BY
    repository_language,
    repository_name) repos
ON
  repos.repository_name = comments.repo_name
GROUP BY
  repos.repository_language
HAVING
  total > 50000
ORDER BY
  per DESC
IGNORE CASE

items.question: Which country, besides the United States, was most mentioned in relation to South Africa last year?
items.sql:
SELECT
  other.country,
  COUNT(*) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    ccode,
    other
  FROM (
    SELECT
      Actor1Code AS ccode,
      Actor2Code AS other,
      Year
    FROM
      [gdelt-bq:full.events]) cc1,
    (
    SELECT
      Actor1Code AS other,
      Actor2Code AS ccode,
      Year
    FROM
      [gdelt-bq:full.events]) cc2
  WHERE
    Year = 2015) events
JOIN
  [gdelt-bq:extra.countryinfo] country
ON
  country.iso3 = events.ccode
JOIN
  [gdelt-bq:extra.countryinfo] other
ON
  events.other = other.iso3
WHERE
  country.country = 'South Afica' 
  AND other.country != 'United States'
GROUP BY
  country.country,
  other.country
ORDER BY
  total DESC
IGNORE CASE

items.question: What was the most popular atari game on Wikipedia last month?
items.sql:
SELECT
  topic_wiki.name AS name,
  SUM(requests) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    topic.mid AS mid,
    topic.name AS name,
    REPLACE(REPLACE(wiki.title, '$0028', '('), '$0029', ')') AS title
  FROM (
    SELECT
      mid,
      name
    FROM
      [freebase_tags.atari_games]) topic
  JOIN (
    SELECT
      REGEXP_REPLACE(REGEXP_REPLACE(obj, '/wikipedia/en/', ''), '/wikipedia/id/', '') AS title,
      sub AS mid
    FROM
      [fh-bigquery:freebase20140119.triples_nolang]
    WHERE
      obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/en'
      OR obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/id'
      AND pred = '/type/object/key') wiki
  ON
    wiki.mid = topic.mid) topic_wiki
JOIN
  [fh-bigquery:wikipedia.pagecounts_201602] views
ON
  views.title = topic_wiki.title
GROUP BY
  mid,
  name
ORDER BY
  total DESC
LIMIT
  10
IGNORE CASE

items.question: Which country was mentioned the most in /r/soccer in the past month?
items.sql:
SELECT
  topic.name,
  COUNT(UNIQUE(comments.id)) AS total
FROM
  [freebase_tags.countries] topic
CROSS JOIN (
  SELECT
    id,
    body
  FROM
    [fh-bigquery:reddit_comments.2016_01]
  WHERE
    subreddit = 'socccer') comments
WHERE
  comments.body CONTAINS CONCAT(' ', topic.name, ' ')
GROUP BY
  topic.name,
ORDER BY
  total DESC IGNORE CASE

SELECT
  topic_wiki.name AS name,
  SUM(requests) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    topic.mid AS mid,
    topic.name AS name,
    REPLACE(REPLACE(wiki.title, '$0028', '('), '$0029', ')') AS title
  FROM (
    SELECT
      mid,
      name
    FROM
      [freebase_tags.GOP]) topic
  JOIN (
    SELECT
      REGEXP_REPLACE(REGEXP_REPLACE(obj, '/wikipedia/en/', ''), '/wikipedia/id/', '') AS title,
      sub AS mid
    FROM
      [fh-bigquery:freebase20140119.triples_nolang]
    WHERE
      obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/en'
      OR obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/id'
      AND pred = '/type/object/key') wiki
  ON
    wiki.mid = topic.mid) topic_wiki
JOIN
  [fh-bigquery:wikipedia.pagecounts_201602] views
ON
  views.title = topic_wiki.title
GROUP BY
  mid,
  name
ORDER BY
  total DESC
LIMIT
  10
IGNORE CASE

  GROUP BY

items.question: Which states subreddit mentioned glamping the most in the past year?
items.sql:
SELECT
  states.state AS state,
  SUM(CASE WHEN REGEXP_MATCH(body, r'(?i)\b(glamping)\b') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 10000 / COUNT(*) AS per
FROM (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM
    TABLE_QUERY([fh-bigquery:reddit_comments], 'regexp_match(table_id, "^2016")')) comments
JOIN
  [subreddits.states] states
ON
  states.subreddit = comments.subreddit
GROUP BY
  state
ORDER BY
  per DESC IGNORE CASE
